life has changed so much lately its unexplainable. I am no longer a sophmore. I would have to say my sophmore year was probably the year i changed dramatically. I lost friends that wouldnt have lasted. If they couldnt deal with the years. I gained friends that i care dearly about. I made bonds stronger with others. I realized whats its like to be loved and not love and love someone. I realized how much i adore being christian and how much i love my music. I am OCD and ADD. I am scared about the upcoming year. Junior year is the year you decide what your future will be. You either stay here and create a life or you choose a college not here and experience life on your own. I am excited but also scared. My life today at this very moment is the best it has been in awhile. I have friends who i care for dearly i ahve a boyfriend who i positively love with all of my heart. I have ajob that i can count on i have my religion to guide me through problems and i have my family still..... together. I love my life at this moment this exact moment in time.
